Title: Polynomial Time Approximation of Dense Weighted Instances of MAX-CUT  
Author: W. Fernandez de la Vega M. Karpinski 
Note: Research partially supported by the ESPRIT BR Grants 7097 and EC-US 030, and by the PROCOPE grant.  by the DFG grant KA 673/4-1, by the ESPRIT BR Grants 7079 and EC-US 030, DIMACS, and by the Max-Planck Research Prize.  
